OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine, warm and sunny day for
OL,6,Fmost of us with the strong sunshine
OL,7,Fgiving very high UV levels, although
OL,8,Fsome fair weather cloudy likely at
OL,9,Ftimes. Lighter winds than on Friday,
OL,10,Falthough sea breezes likely developing
OL,11,Finto the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry night will then follow
OL,14,Fwith light winds for all. A mix of
OL,15,Fsome cloud and clear spells. Turning
OL,16,Frather chilly under prolonged clear
OL,17,Fskies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
