OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FSunday will be a fine day with
OL,6,Flight winds and a mix of fair weather
OL,7,Fcloud and sunny spells. Feeling warmer
OL,8,Ffor all. Sea breezes developing into
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,12,Fwith sunny spells on Monday. Cloudier
OL,13,Ffrom Tuesday with a some showers at
OL,14,Ftimes. Turning a little windier,
OL,15,Fespecially by Wednesday. Remaining
OL,16,Frather warm throughout.
